    "description": "課程提供簡單的印尼語會話，簡單的印尼語語法，簡單的印尼語造句，讓學生可以簡單的聽、說、讀、寫印尼語，也能認識一些印尼傳統文化，印尼美食， 印尼的觀光經典及奇特色。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.課程介紹－認識印尼<br>2.瞭解印尼語言基本發音結構<br>3.基本問候、自我介紹<br>4.認識家庭成員稱呼<br>5.禮貌用語、社交用語<br>6.時間、日期、數字<br>7.印尼美食、傳統服飾與印尼文化<br>8.印尼建築、觀光景點與觀光用語<br>9.印尼宗教、文化<br>9.印尼交通、簡單會話<br>10.印尼教育、簡單會話<br>",
        "en": "1. Introduction of Course Material, Introduction to Indonesia<br>2. Basic Indonesia Pronunciation<br>3. Greetings and self introduction<br>4. Name of family members<br>5. Simple sentence<br>6. Indonesian cuisine, traditional clothing and culture of Indonesia<br>7. Indonesia architecture, tourism, and language used in traveling<br>8. Indonesia traffic and easy conversation<br>9. How to say how you feel<br>10. Indonesia religion and our culture about religion"
